				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\mathbf {x}_{\min } < \mathbf {x}_{\max }$$\end{document} element-wise) and (2) the autoencoder is calibrated (Pc=0\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
