				\begin{document}$$D(\mathbf {x}_i,\mathbf {x}_j)<T$$\end{document} where D is a distance function. To determine a safe inlier, at least two data points (xi,xj\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
