The size of the sliding window for MCOD and STORM2 was W = 10,000. The results of COD are not reported for W = 10,000, because of a very long computation time. For comparison, the results of our proposed method (AE, hidden neurons h∈{2,10}\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
